 car and you’re not sure how old the battery is, or you’re wondering about your battery’s health, bring it in to a service centre for an instant diagnosis. Our mechanical team members use an advanced battery tester that measures how much of the material inside your battery is working. The yes/no score gives you an accurate answer and a bit of peace of mind.</p><p>If you think you might be experiencing battery trouble, bring your battery in to a&nbsp;Kal Tire location&nbsp;near you for a free battery test.</p>",
