r wheel was bent, we can order you a new one.</p><p><span style=\"color: black;\">If your tires are out of balance, we’ll balance them with wheel weights so you can get back to driving straight and smooth. We’ll also perform a&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.kaltire.com/en/wheel-alignment/\" target=\"_self\" data-link-type=\"external\" data-link-label=\"computerized wheel alignment\">computerized wheel alignment</a><span style=\"color: black;\"> to&nbsp;ensure you’re ready for the road with centred and straight wheels and steering wheel. </span></p><p><span style=\"color: black;\">Even if you’ve hit a hard bump and your wheel wasn’t bent, it’s a good idea to bring your vehicle in because you may still need an alignment.</span></p>",
